## Next Steps for the User

To activate Web Analytics on Vercel:
1. Navigate to your Vercel dashboard
2. Select "Analytics" from the sidebar
3. Choose your project
4. Click the "Enable" button in the header
5. Deploy your project to Vercel

The code is already configured correctly and will start tracking analytics automatically once enabled in the Vercel dashboard.

